short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Local storage items builder for web tests

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Internal tool to customized tests for websites who run tests that read theirs configuration from local storage.
This tool create the local storage set command with all the necessary data for every test.
